EKS Nodes vs EKS Managed NodeGroup
K8 version needs to be updated
Deploy security patches
EC2 AMIs need to be updated
Create AMIs
During the update Application will be DOWN 
and we need to orchestrate HA 


AWS EKS Managed NodeGroup Automate to provisoning
and lifecyle managment

Create and Manage EC2 Workers for you
● Amazon releases AMIs with bug fix, security patches for 
EKS Worker Nodes
○ Custom AMIs not supported (As of April, 2020)
● Automated deployment of updated AMIs with security 
patches, CVEs
○ No app downtime
○ No overhead of user managed orchestration
○ Auto scaling group is used behind the scene